{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"alias":"future-relative-limpet","description":"## Why\nInit-time `_migrate_*`/`_ensure_*` steps only run at init/re-init, so config fixes never\nreach already-existing stores. A first-class idempotent ensure-registry generalizes them\n(School B desired-state) so every non-hot entry point can converge an existing install.\n\n## What\nCreate `src/rebar/_store/ensures.py`: a registry of ensure units, each with a stable id and\na **check-then-act** callable that no-ops when already converged and reports `changed`/`ok`.\n`run_ensures()` runs ALL units unconditionally, returns per-unit results + failures, and\nrecords the set of cleanly-applied ids to the applied-set marker (WS2 owns the marker format).\nMigrate the 5 current init-time steps: gc-config, merge=ours driver, gitattributes\n(check-then-commit — the only step producing a git commit), scratch-exclude, env-id seed.\nWire `init_core` to call `run_ensures()` instead of the hand-listed steps.\n\n## Scope\nIn: `ensures.py`, the 5 migrated units, `run_ensures()`, init wiring. Out: the write-path hint\n(WS2), fsck/server-startup wiring (WS3), docs (WS4).\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] `src/rebar/_store/ensures.py` holds a registry of ensure units, each with a stable id + check-then-act callable reporting changed/ok\n- [ ] All 5 init-time steps migrated in; `init_core` calls `run_ensures()` (no behavior regression at init)\n- [ ] Each unit is idempotent: a second `run_ensures()` on a converged store makes zero changes and zero git commits\n- [ ] `run_ensures()` runs every unit unconditionally (never gated on the marker) and returns per-unit changed/ok + failures\n- [ ] gitattributes unit checks the tree before committing (no empty/no-op commits on the shared tickets branch)","id":"ec29-af41-884e-420d","parent_id":"9ccb-27ee-24dd-4944","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"story","title":"WS1: ensure-registry (ensures.py) + migrate 5 check-then-act steps + init wiring"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783569037995072001,"uuid":"05a2616e-6707-4b78-a775-177a52a7f7c5"}